nodes.text: Bo Bahaahaa was a Gotal who, along with Klen Hoofber, was in a standoff with IG-88. IG-88 claimed to have a bounty on Ba Bohaahaa, mispronouncing the Gotal's name to mislead Hoofber, who believed that in betraying and stunning Bahaahaa would share the bounty with IG-88.
In one panel, Bo Bahaahaa's named is misspelled as Ba Bohaahaa.
